<i>noun</i>: 힐난 [힐란], 평론 [평ː논], 평 [평ː], 타박 [타ː박], 지탄 [지탄], 지적 [지적], 악담 [악땀], 손가락질 [손까락찔], 비평 [비ː평], 비판 [비ː판], 비난 [비ː난], 만평 [만ː평], 논평 [논평], 거론 [거ː론] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>힐난 [힐란]</dt><br>
<dd>blame; criticism; reproach</dd><br>
<dd>트집을 잡아 마음이 편하지 않을 정도로 따지고 듦.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of finding fault with someone in such a persistent and argumentative manner that it upsets the person.</dd><br>
<dt>평론 [평ː논]</dt><br>
<dd>critique; criticism; review</dd><br>
<dd>사물의 가치, 좋은 점과 나쁜 점, 뛰어난 점과 부족한 점 등을 평가하여 말함. 또는 그런 글.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of evaluating and commenting on an object's value, whether it is right or wrong, its strengths and weaknesses, etc., or such a piece of writing.</dd><br>
<dt>평 [평ː]</dt><br>
<dd>criticism; comment; review</dd><br>
<dd>좋고 나쁨, 잘하고 못함, 옳고 그름 등을 평가함. 또는 그런 말.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of evaluating whether something is good or bad, well-done or poorly-done, right or wrong, etc., or such a remark.</dd><br>
<dt>타박 [타ː박]</dt><br>
<dd>finding fault with; criticism</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람의 실수나 결함을 나무라거나 핀잔함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of blaming or scolding someone for his/her mistake or fault.</dd><br>
<dt>지탄 [지탄]</dt><br>
<dd>criticism; censure</dd><br>
<dd>잘못을 꼭 집어 비난함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of pointing out one's mistake or fault and criticizing it.</dd><br>
<dt>지적 [지적]</dt><br>
<dd>1. indication</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것을 꼭 집어서 분명하게 가리킴.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of singling out or pointing out someone or something.</dd><br>
<dd>2. criticism; comment</dd><br>
<dd>잘못된 점이나 고쳐야 할 점을 가리켜 말함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of pointing out something that is wrong or needs to be fixed.</dd><br>
<dt>악담 [악땀]</dt><br>
<dd>curse; malediction; criticism</dd><br>
<dd>남을 헐뜯거나 남에게 나쁜 일이 일어나도록 저주하는 말.</dd><br>
<dd>A remark to criticize or wishing bad luck for someone.</dd><br>
<dt>손가락질 [손까락찔]</dt><br>
<dd>1. finger-pointing; pointing</dd><br>
<dd>손가락으로 무엇을 가리키는 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of indicating something with a finger.</dd><br>
<dd>2. criticism</dd><br>
<dd>남을 흉보는 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of finding fault with others.</dd><br>
<dt>비평 [비ː평]</dt><br>
<dd>criticism; critique; review; comment</dd><br>
<dd>옳고 그름, 아름다움과 추함 등을 분석하여 사물의 가치를 논함.</dd><br>
<dd>A discussion of an object's values by examining its various properties.</dd><br>
<dt>비판 [비ː판]</dt><br>
<dd>criticism; critical judgment; rebuke</dd><br>
<dd>무엇에 대해 자세히 따져 옳고 그름을 밝히거나 잘못된 점을 지적함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of examining something closely and making a judgment between right and wrong, or pointing out what is wrong.</dd><br>
<dt>비난 [비ː난]</dt><br>
<dd>blame; condemnation; criticism</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람의 잘못이나 결점에 대하여 나쁘게 말함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of speaking unfavorably about others' mistakes or flaws.</dd><br>
<dt>만평 [만ː평]</dt><br>
<dd>1. criticism; comment</dd><br>
<dd>일정한 형식이나 체계를 갖추지 않고 인물이나 사회를 자유롭게 비판하는 글.</dd><br>
<dd>A writing that criticizes a certain figure or society freely without a certain format or structure.</dd><br>
<dd>2. satirical cartoon</dd><br>
<dd>인물이나 사회를 풍자하여 비판하는 내용을 담은 만화.</dd><br>
<dd>A cartoon that contains satirical criticism of a certain figure or society.</dd><br>
<dt>논평 [논평]</dt><br>
<dd>criticism; comment; review</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 글이나 말, 사건 등에 대하여 옳고 그름이나 좋고 나쁨 등을 판단하여 드러내 알림. 또는 그런 비평.</dd><br>
<dd>Judging and disclosing whether a remark, written statement, incident, etc. is right, wrong, good, bad, etc., or this kind of criticism.</dd><br>
<dt>거론 [거ː론]</dt><br>
<dd>discussion; criticism</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 것을 이야기의 주제나 문제로 삼아 논의함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of bringing up or mentioning something as a subject of discussion or an object of criticism.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>